Introduction

Tracking System 

Education

This system operates within the education domain, focusing on assisting students in managing academic tasks and deadlines effectively.

Problem Statement

Students often struggle to manage multiple assignments across different modules using complex platforms such as Blackboard. This leads to missed deadlines, poor time management, and increased stress.

System Purpose

The system aims to provide a simple and centralized platform where students can track assignments, receive reminders, and manage their academic responsibilities efficiently.

Individual Scope

The system is feasible as an individual project because:

It has limited but meaningful features
It can be developed using basic web technologies
It does not require complex integrations initially

The focus will be on core features such as assignment tracking, notifications, and task management.
